message.body: Hey Jen! I'm actually going to be tight on time because I still have to take a shower since I still smell like cigarettes. I'm sorry, maybe Sam could pick you up?
Jeff is picking her up an don't want to impose ourselves on them. It's okay! We'll take the train! Ain't no thing but a chicken wing.
Oh Okay, sorry again. I'll see you soon!
Hey Jen! I already texted Sam and told her I'm running behind so I'll be late for dinner. Sorry!!!
It's okay sammy. We're here so the reservation is safe.
No worries. We're here and Sam's running late too.
